{"id":179,"date":"2021-07-14T13:05:48","date_gmt":"2021-07-14T20:05:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/?page_id=179"},"modified":"2024-03-15T10:36:31","modified_gmt":"2024-03-15T16:36:31","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-hero-inside\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-30 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1367\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1641\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2.jpg\" style=\"object-position:29% 48%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"29% 48%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2-1600x1068.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Header-Hero-I70Project-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why<br>MYR Group<sub>Over a century of connecting power to people<\/sub><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#learn-more\">Learn More <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-316\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/arrow-down.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-right-image-content\" style=\"min-height:1013px;aspect-ratio:unset;\" id=\"learn-more\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1365\" height=\"2048\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2194\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2.jpg\" style=\"object-position:52% 51%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"52% 51%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2.jpg 1365w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2-1066x1600.jpg 1066w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Leader-In-Construction-Anetelope-Juniper-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline has-black-color has-text-color\">A recognized leader in electrical construction<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MYR Group Inc. (MYR Group) and its subsidiaries have delivered some of the largest, most notable electrical infrastructure and commercial and industrial projects. Our integrated solutions, extensive expertise, and comprehensive approach to providing superior electrical construction services drive strong project outcomes with exceptional customer service and value. It\u2019s why MYR Group has been recognized year after year as one of the top five specialty electrical contracting firms by Engineering News-Record. This legacy of success can be attributed to our skilled and dedicated workforce, our strategic business initiatives, and our continual drive to improve and adapt.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since 1891, MYR Group (publicly traded on NASDAQ under the symbol MYRG) and our family of companies have operated responsibly with our mission, vision, and values at the core of everything we do.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-dark-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-left-image-content\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1644\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Our-Subsidiaries-South-Station-005-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline\">Our Subsidiaries<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With 9,000+ employees, MYR Group subsidiaries have a long history of success. Through its subsidiaries, MYR Group provides unique, comprehensive transmission and distribution, and industrial electrical construction services to customers throughout the U.S. and Canada.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/subsidiaries\/\">Learn More<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover seventy-vh\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-60 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2016\" height=\"1512\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2598\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16.jpg\" style=\"object-position:63% 52%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"63% 52%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16.jpg 2016w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Hurricane-Ida-16-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2016px) 100vw, 2016px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><sup>YOUR Clean Energy Transformation Partner<\/sup>DELIVERING SUSTAINABLE SOLUTIONS TO OUR CLIENTS IN THIS EVOLVING clean ENERGY LANDSCAPE<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><br><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section mission-vision-values-wrapper has-myrgroup-gray-dark-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-bottom is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><sup>Our Mission, Vision &amp; Values<\/sup>Deeply rooted in our <span class=\"has-inline-color has-myrgroup-blue-color\">culture<\/span> and strategy for the <span class=\"has-inline-color has-myrgroup-blue-color\">future<\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1415\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4-1600x1415.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1647\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4-1600x1415.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4-1024x906.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4-768x679.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4-1536x1358.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Mission-Vision-Values-4.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline\">Our mission<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To provide superior specialty contracting services by creating mutually rewarding relationships in a safe, sustainable, inclusive, and inspiring environment.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline\">Our Vision<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating connections that empower people.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group values-intro-wrapper has-myrgroup-blue-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-white-color\">The following values guide us, inspire us, and help us shape our behavior and culture<\/mark>:<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns values-wrapper is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-299\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_safety.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>Safety<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At MYR Group, Safety is Life. It sustains our employees, customers, company, and the environment. Because of our commitments to safety our culture embraces constant innovation and improvement in our safety practices as the catalyst that set us apart today, tomorrow, and beyond.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-297\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_respect.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>Respect<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In our day-to-day endeavors, respect sets the standard for how we interact with each other, our clients, and the communities we work in. This standard establishes a positive, productive, and inclusive work environment.&nbsp;Internally it contributes to our ability to attract and retain the best; externally it enhances our relationships with our clients, vendors, and investors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-298\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_responsiveness.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>Responsiveness<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We must strive to provide timely, thorough, and accurate solutions and alternatives not only in times of crisis, but also during day-to-day operations. The fundamental essence of our success lies in our ability to respond rapidly.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-294\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_creativity.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>Creativity<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Creativity stimulates an environment rich with opportunity and the potential for&nbsp;positive growth. It explores new ideas, values original thinking, fosters better ways of doing business, embraces innovation, and attracts quality people. These attributes lead to expanded opportunities that help to position us as an industry leader.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns values-wrapper is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-296\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_integriy.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>INTEGRITY<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our commitment to integrity guides our actions and builds trust which enhances our overall reputation and leadership effectiveness. We will ensure our actions and processes incorporate social and environmental stewardship to support a sustainable future for all stakeholders.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-295\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_initiative.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>INITIATIVE<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Initiative is an essential component of our value system because it encourages people to take responsibility and action when not required or expected. It rewards those who are self-starters and leaders that continually overcome obstacles and work toward constant improvement.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-300\" style=\"width: NaNpx\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/icons_teamwork.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>TEAMWORK<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By combining our skills and resources through shared responsibility, effective communication, and common goals, we achieve a distinct competitive environment. This is accomplished by recruiting and retaining a diverse workforce that is highly communicative and collaborative.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-dark-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-left-image-content\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1162\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1648\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126.jpg\" style=\"object-position:60% 66%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"60% 66%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126-1024x581.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126-1600x908.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126-768x436.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Community-Involvement-WPE-2-1-e1638286105126-1536x872.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-default\"><sup>COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT<\/sup>building strong, resilient, and sustainable communities<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our core values set the foundation for how we conduct ourselves as a responsible business in the communities we live and serve. That\u2019s why our company prioritizes corporate social responsibility and creating ways for our employees to contribute to causes that they care about. Coming together for the greater good promotes positive change, so we are proud to invest our time and energy to make a difference in the world around us. Through charitable giving, volunteer efforts, and local partnerships we support meaningful causes that protect, preserve, and enhance our society.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-very-light-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns timeline-wrapper is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column timeline-image-wrapper is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section footer-call-to-action\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-myrgroup-blue-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-white-color has-text-color\">Strength in Our legacy and success are directly attributed to our network of companies<\/h2>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/subsidiaries\/\">LEARN MORE<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Mission, Vision &amp; ValuesDeeply rooted in our culture and strategy for the future Our mission To provide superior specialty contracting services by creating mutually rewarding relationships in a safe, sustainable, inclusive, and inspiring environment.&nbsp; Our Vision Creating connections that empower people.&nbsp; The following values guide us, inspire us, and help us shape our behavior [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":10,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-179","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/179"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-json\